song.title: Damn, Harry!
song.info:
An entry for the Nectarine "Style Copy Compo", where the goal was to emulate the style of another scene artist. I attempted to copy the big beat styles of D Fast (Harry Damm), but everyone thought it was Press Play On Tape. 4th place of 5 entries.
Sunvox, with lots of samples.
CC attributions, all from freesound.org: Voice shouts by unfa clap by opm record scratch by hello_flowers
